    "In other words, the numbers presented in journals and conference proceedings do not reflect how successful a system will be when applied in practice.",
    "Second, metrics guide the scientific progress in the field; flawed metric use can lead to entirely futile resource investment and infeasible research directions while obscuring true scientific advancements.",
